sequenceDiagram
    participant browser
    participant server

    browser->>server: GET /exampleapp/
    activate server
    server-->>browser: HTML document
    deactivate server

    Note right of browser: Browser parses HTML and discovers assets

    browser->>server: GET /exampleapp/main.css
    activate server
    server-->>browser: main.css file
    deactivate server

    browser->>server: GET /exampleapp/spa.js
    activate server
    server-->>browser: spa.js file
    deactivate server

    Note right of browser: Browser executes spa.js

    browser->>server: GET /exampleapp/data.json
    activate server
    server-->>browser: JSON array of notes
    deactivate server

    Note right of browser: spa.js parses JSON and calls redrawNotes()
    Note right of browser: redrawNotes() renders list with existing notes

    Note right of browser: Page is fully loaded and interactive